name: Krayt Dragon Bones (V)
Lore: 'Tusken Raiders, Jawas and other desert dwellers believe that krayt dragon bones possess mystical powers that can bring good or bad luck.',
Text: 'Deploy on table.  Womp Rats are not [Selective Creature].  Once per turn, may deploy a creature (except a parasite) or a dewback from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  Your ferocious creatures are deploy -2 and ferocity +1.  Whenever you retrieve Force because a creatue has eaten a card, you need only use X-2 Force for Aim High (to a minimum of 1). (Immune to Alter.)',
